org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.parameters.library.roi

Class Margin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.extensions.parameters.library.roi.Margin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JIPipeParameterCollection

    public class Margin
extends Object
implements JIPipeParameterCollection
    Parameter that allows users to define a rectangle ROI. Users can define a rectangle the classical way (x, y, width, height), but also other ways.
